         <div xml:id="alalal-d95574"><!-- l2d35dt -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-d95574-Hd1e99">Divisio Textus</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d95574-d1e101">
               <cb ed="#Bc" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="20"/>DIVISIO TEXTUS.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d95574-d1e108">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="21"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-d95574-Qd1e112"> Post haec videndum est, quid sit 
pec<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="22"/>catum, etc. </quote>
               <cb ed="#Bc" n="c"/>
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="23"/>Hic incipit agere de peccato. Et 
divi<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="24"/>ditur in tres partes : in quarum prima
<lb ed="#Bc" n="25"/>tangit quid sit peccatum diffinitive et
<lb ed="#Bc" n="26"/>realiter. In secunda autem determinat,
<lb ed="#Bc" n="27"/>utrum peccatum habeat rationem pene
<lb ed="#Bc" n="28"/>vel non ? in distinctione XXXVI, ibi,
<lb ed="#Bc" n="29"/>A, <quote xml:id="alalal-d95574-Qd1e134"> Sciendum est, etc. </quote> In tertia que-
<pb ed="#Bc" n="561"/>
               <cb ed="#Bc" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="1"/>rit, Utrum actus peccatorum sunt a Deo,
<lb ed="#Bc" n="2"/>vel non ? in distinctione XXXVII, ibi,
<lb ed="#Bc" n="3"/>A, <quote xml:id="alalal-d95574-Qd1e147"> Sunt et alii plures, etc.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d95574-d1e150">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="4"/>Presens autem lectio continet quatuor
<lb ed="#Bc" n="5"/>artes : in quarum prima Magister dat
<lb ed="#Bc" n="6"/>tres diffinitiones de peccato. In secunda,
<lb ed="#Bc" n="7"/>ponit rationes diversarum opinionum ad
<lb ed="#Bc" n="8"/>quid sit peccatum secundum rem et 
sub<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="9"/>stantiam, ibi, B, <quote xml:id="alalal-d95574-Qd1e165"> Quocirca diversitatis
<lb ed="#Bc" n="10"/>hujus, etc. </quote> In tertia,. tangit rationes
<lb ed="#Bc" n="11"/>eorum qui dicunt omne peccatum in
<lb ed="#Bc" n="12"/>quantum est, a Deo esse, et objicil 
con<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="13"/>tra eos, et solvit, ibi, D, <quote xml:id="alalal-d95574-Qd1e176"> Quidam
<lb ed="#Bc" n="14"/>autem diligenter, etc. </quote> In quarta 
que<lb break="no" ed="#Bc" n="15"/>rit, Gum peccatum sit corruptio boni,
<lb ed="#Bc" n="16"/>utrum corrumpat bonum in quantum
<lb ed="#Bc" n="17"/>est, vel in quantum actus est, vel in
<lb ed="#Bc" n="18"/>guantum peccatum est ? ibi, K, <quote xml:id="alalal-d95574-Qd1e190"> Potest
<lb ed="#Bc" n="19"/>etiam queri ab eisdem, Cum peccatum,
<lb ed="#Bc" n="20"/>etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-d95574-d1e198">
               <lb ed="#Bc" n="21"/>Et per hoc patet sententia.
</p>
